==Polish==

===Phrase===
'''[[dzień]] [[dobry]]'''
#[[Good day]] (in direct translation) 
#[[Good morning]]
#[[Good afternoon]]

A Polish formal greeting said when meeting somebody during most of the day (equivalent of English 'good morning' and 'good afternoon').  

See also:
[[dobry wieczór]]

